<!-- §8 Why people are buying — problem this solves -->
<h2>Why Weighted Blankets Aren't Perfect for Hot Sleepers</h2>
<p>Weighted blankets deliver amazing deep pressure therapy, but they trap body heat like a furnace. For hot sleepers, night sweats, and anyone in warm climates, the calming benefits get completely offset by waking up drenched. That's where compression sheets come in — they deliver the same cocoon-like pressure without the heat buildup.</p>
