<!-- §9 What is [Product]? -->
<h2>What Is a Sensory Compression Bed Sheet?</h2>
<p>A sensory compression bed sheet is a stretchy, elastic fabric that wraps around your mattress and pulls tight like a cocoon. Unlike weighted blankets (which use gravity), compression sheets apply even pressure across your entire body through the stretch of the material itself. The Ntomtuex is made from breathable polyester, so it stays cool while providing that full-body hug sensation that calms the nervous system — especially effective for people with sensory processing differences, anxiety, and anyone who craves that "tucked in tight" feeling.</p>

